
UPDATE products SET description = CASE title
WHEN 'Classic Cotton T-Shirt' THEN 'This premium 100% combed cotton crew neck t-shirt is crafted for everyday comfort and style. Available in a range of solid colors, it features reinforced stitching at the shoulders and hem for long-lasting durability. The pre-shrunk fabric ensures a consistent fit wash after wash, while the breathable weave keeps you cool in Indian summers. Perfect for casual outings, college, or layering under a jacket.'
WHEN 'Slim Fit Denim Jeans' THEN 'These dark indigo wash slim fit jeans are made from premium stretchable denim that moves with you throughout the day. Featuring a mid-rise waist, five-pocket styling, and a tapered leg, they offer a modern silhouette without sacrificing comfort. The fade-resistant wash maintains its rich color even after multiple washes. Ideal for pairing with kurtas, t-shirts, or formal shirts for a smart-casual look.'
WHEN 'Casual Linen Shirt' THEN 'Stay cool and stylish with this breathable pure linen shirt, perfect for the hot Indian summer months. The relaxed regular fit features a button-down collar, chest pocket, and adjustable roll-up sleeves. The natural linen fabric allows excellent airflow and gets softer with every wash. Whether you are heading to the office, a weekend brunch, or a beach vacation, this shirt keeps you comfortable and looking sharp.'
WHEN 'Cotton Hoodie Unisex' THEN 'This cozy fleece-lined pullover hoodie is designed for unisex wear and features a spacious kangaroo pocket and an adjustable drawstring hood. Made from a premium cotton-polyester blend, it provides warmth during chilly winter evenings and monsoon weather. The ribbed cuffs and hem ensure a snug fit, while the brushed interior lining offers exceptional softness against your skin. Available in multiple trending colors.'
WHEN 'Running Sneakers' THEN 'Engineered for performance and comfort, these lightweight mesh running shoes feature a cushioned EVA midsole that absorbs impact with every stride. The breathable upper mesh keeps your feet cool during long runs, while the textured rubber outsole provides excellent grip on both wet and dry surfaces. Whether you are training for a marathon or going for a morning jog in the park, these sneakers deliver unmatched support and style.'
WHEN 'Printed Ethnic Kurta' THEN 'Celebrate Indian craftsmanship with this beautifully block-printed cotton kurta featuring traditional Rajasthani motifs. Made from soft, breathable cotton fabric, it is perfect for festivals, puja ceremonies, or casual ethnic wear. The kurta features a mandarin collar, side slits, and three-quarter sleeves for a classic silhouette. Each piece is hand-printed by skilled artisans, making every kurta unique.'
WHEN 'Aviator Sunglasses' THEN 'These classic UV400 polarized aviator sunglasses combine timeless style with superior eye protection. The lightweight metal frame features adjustable silicone nose pads for a comfortable, custom fit. Polarized lenses reduce glare from roads, water, and snow, making them perfect for driving, beach trips, and outdoor activities. The scratch-resistant coating ensures long-lasting clarity. Comes with a premium hard case and microfiber cleaning cloth.'
WHEN 'Leather Belt Classic' THEN 'Crafted from genuine full-grain leather, this classic belt features a brushed nickel buckle that adds a touch of sophistication to any outfit. The leather develops a beautiful patina over time, making it uniquely yours. With precise stitching along the edges and multiple adjustment holes, it provides a secure and comfortable fit. Versatile enough for both formal business attire and casual weekend looks.'
WHEN 'Canvas Backpack 25L' THEN 'This rugged 25-liter canvas backpack is built for students, professionals, and travelers alike. It features a padded laptop compartment that fits up to 15.6-inch laptops, multiple organizer pockets, and reinforced water-resistant canvas material. The padded shoulder straps and breathable back panel ensure comfort during long commutes. With its vintage-inspired design and durable YKK zippers, this backpack is both functional and stylish.'
WHEN 'Sports Track Pants' THEN 'These moisture-wicking sports track pants are designed for athletes and fitness enthusiasts who demand performance and comfort. Made from quick-dry polyester fabric with four-way stretch, they feature zippered side pockets, an elastic waistband with drawstring, and tapered legs with zip ankles. Perfect for gym sessions, morning jogs, or casual everyday wear.'
WHEN 'Wireless Bluetooth Earbuds' THEN 'Experience immersive audio with these premium wireless Bluetooth earbuds featuring active noise cancellation technology. With a combined 24-hour battery life, deep bass drivers, and crystal-clear call quality, they are perfect for commuting, working out, or relaxing at home. The ergonomic design with multiple ear tip sizes ensures a secure and comfortable fit. IPX5 water resistance makes them sweat and splash-proof.'
WHEN 'Noise Cancelling Headphones' THEN 'Immerse yourself in pure sound with these over-ear headphones featuring advanced Active Noise Cancellation technology. The 40mm custom drivers deliver rich, balanced audio across all frequencies, while the plush memory foam ear cushions provide hours of comfortable listening. With a massive 30-hour battery life, built-in microphone for calls, and foldable design for easy portability, these headphones are perfect for flights, office work, and studio sessions.'
WHEN 'Smart Fitness Watch' THEN 'Take control of your health and fitness with this advanced smartwatch featuring continuous heart rate monitoring, SpO2 blood oxygen tracking, built-in GPS, and over 100 workout modes. The vibrant AMOLED display is clearly visible even in direct sunlight, while the 7-day battery life keeps you going all week. Track sleep patterns, receive notifications, and monitor stress levels from your wrist. IP68 water resistant for swimming and rain.'
WHEN 'Portable Bluetooth Speaker' THEN 'Bring the party anywhere with this powerful waterproof Bluetooth speaker delivering immersive 360-degree sound. With a 12-hour playtime on a single charge, IPX7 waterproof rating, and rugged dustproof design, it is built for outdoor adventures from pool parties to camping trips. The dual passive radiators produce deep, punchy bass, while the built-in microphone allows hands-free calling. Connect two speakers for stereo sound.'
WHEN 'Mechanical Gaming Keyboard' THEN 'Dominate your gaming sessions with this RGB backlit mechanical keyboard featuring responsive blue switches that provide satisfying tactile feedback and a distinct click. The aircraft-grade aluminum top plate ensures durability, while the per-key RGB lighting with 16.8 million colors lets you customize your setup. Anti-ghosting with N-key rollover ensures every keystroke is registered during intense gameplay. Includes detachable wrist rest and braided USB-C cable.'
WHEN 'Wireless Mouse Ergonomic' THEN 'Say goodbye to wrist strain with this ergonomically designed wireless mouse featuring a natural hand position that reduces fatigue during long work sessions. The silent click mechanism eliminates distracting noise, while the adjustable DPI allows precise cursor control. The reliable 2.4GHz wireless connection provides lag-free performance up to 10 meters, and the 18-month battery life means fewer interruptions.'
WHEN '10000mAh Power Bank' THEN 'Never run out of power on the go with this slim, lightweight 10000mAh portable charger. Featuring dual USB-A outputs and a USB-C input/output port, it can charge two devices simultaneously at fast-charging speeds. The LED digital display shows exact remaining battery percentage. With built-in overcharge, over-discharge, and short-circuit protection, your devices are always safe. Perfect for travel, commuting, and emergencies.'
WHEN 'USB-C Fast Charger 65W' THEN 'Power up your entire tech ecosystem with this compact 65W GaN fast charger. The advanced GaN technology delivers maximum power in a remarkably small form factor — 50% smaller than traditional chargers. Compatible with laptops, tablets, smartphones, and Nintendo Switch, it supports PD 3.0 and QC 4.0 protocols. The foldable plug design makes it incredibly travel-friendly. BIS certified for Indian power standards.'
WHEN 'HD Webcam 1080p' THEN 'Upgrade your video calls, online classes, and content creation with this Full HD 1080p webcam. The wide-angle lens captures a 90-degree field of view, while the built-in dual stereo microphones with noise reduction ensure your voice comes through clearly. Auto light correction adapts to any lighting condition. Plug-and-play USB connectivity means no drivers needed — just connect and start streaming in crystal-clear quality.'
WHEN 'Smart LED Desk Lamp' THEN 'Transform your workspace with this sleek touch-controlled LED desk lamp featuring five adjustable brightness levels and three color temperature modes. The flexible gooseneck allows you to direct light exactly where you need it, while the built-in USB charging port keeps your phone powered up. The flicker-free LED technology reduces eye strain during long study or work sessions. The modern minimalist design complements any desk setup.'
WHEN 'Atomic Habits' THEN 'In this groundbreaking book, James Clear reveals the proven system for building good habits and breaking bad ones. Drawing on biology, psychology, and neuroscience, Clear shows how tiny changes in behavior can lead to remarkable results over time. The book introduces the Four Laws of Behavior Change framework that makes habit formation simple and actionable. Whether you want to improve your fitness, productivity, or relationships, this book provides the practical strategies you need to transform your life one small habit at a time.'
WHEN 'Rich Dad Poor Dad' THEN 'Robert Kiyosakis personal finance classic challenges everything you thought you knew about money. Through the story of his two dads — his real father and the father of his best friend — Kiyosaki reveals the mindset and financial knowledge that separates the wealthy from everyone else. Learn why the rich dont work for money, how to make money work for you, the importance of financial literacy, and why your house is not an asset. This book has inspired millions worldwide to take control of their financial future.'
WHEN 'The Alchemist' THEN 'Paulo Coelhos enchanting masterpiece tells the story of Santiago, a young Andalusian shepherd who travels from Spain to the Egyptian desert in search of treasure. Along the way, he meets a series of mentors who teach him to listen to his heart, recognize opportunity, and follow his Personal Legend. This timeless tale of self-discovery, courage, and the transformative power of following your dreams has captivated readers across generations and cultures, selling over 65 million copies worldwide.'
WHEN 'Sapiens: A Brief History' THEN 'In this sweeping narrative, historian Yuval Noah Harari takes readers on a fascinating journey through the entire history of humankind — from the emergence of Homo sapiens in Africa to the present. Harari examines how biology and history have shaped our understanding of what it means to be human, exploring the Cognitive Revolution, Agricultural Revolution, and Scientific Revolution. Thought-provoking and deeply researched, Sapiens challenges our fundamental assumptions about human civilization and our place in the world.'
WHEN 'The Psychology of Money' THEN 'Morgan Housels bestselling book explores the strange ways people think about money through 19 short stories. Rather than focusing on formulas and spreadsheets, Housel examines the behavioral and emotional aspects of personal finance. He reveals how your personal history, unique worldview, ego, pride, and marketing influence your financial decisions more than any spreadsheet ever could. This book teaches timeless lessons on wealth, greed, happiness, and the surprising gap between being smart and behaving wisely with money.'
WHEN 'Deep Work by Cal Newport' THEN 'Cal Newport makes a compelling case that the ability to perform deep, focused work is becoming increasingly rare and increasingly valuable in our economy. He presents a rigorous training regimen for developing deep work skills, combining cultural criticism with actionable advice. Learn the four rules of deep work, strategies to eliminate distractions, and techniques used by great minds throughout history. Whether you are a writer, programmer, or business leader, this book will transform how you approach your most important tasks.'
WHEN 'Start With Why' THEN 'Simon Sineks revolutionary framework explains why some leaders and organizations inspire action while others dont. Through real-world examples from Apple to Martin Luther King Jr., Sinek reveals The Golden Circle — a naturally occurring pattern grounded in biology that explains how great leaders think, act, and communicate differently. This book will change how you think about leadership, marketing, and building movements that people want to follow. Essential reading for entrepreneurs and aspiring leaders.'
WHEN 'Ikigai: The Japanese Secret' THEN 'Discover the Japanese concept of ikigai — your reason for being — through the wisdom of the worlds longest-living people in Okinawa, Japan. Authors Hector Garcia and Francesc Miralles interviewed over 100 centenarians to uncover the secrets to their longevity, happiness, and sense of purpose. The book blends philosophy, science, and practical exercises to help you find your own ikigai, reduce stress, build resilience, and live a longer, more fulfilling life. A beautiful, life-changing read.'
WHEN 'Thinking Fast and Slow' THEN 'Nobel laureate Daniel Kahneman takes readers on a groundbreaking tour of the mind, explaining the two systems that drive the way we think — System 1 (fast, intuitive, emotional) and System 2 (slow, deliberate, logical). Through decades of research, Kahneman reveals cognitive biases that affect our judgments and decisions in business, relationships, and everyday life. This landmark work transforms how we understand human rationality, risk assessment, and decision-making. A must-read for anyone who wants to think more clearly.'
WHEN 'The Subtle Art of Not Giving' THEN 'Mark Mansons refreshingly honest self-help book argues that improving our lives requires not doing more, but focusing on less — only caring about what is truly important. Drawing on academic research and personal anecdotes, Manson challenges the culture of toxic positivity and shows that life improvement comes from learning to struggle better, not from avoiding struggle altogether. Provocative, humorous, and brutally honest, this book has resonated with millions who are tired of being told to just think positive.'
ELSE description
END
WHERE category IN ('Apparel', 'Electronics', 'Books');
